            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kethan-krishna-6a4226262/"
            target="_blank"
            ><svg
              class="w-6 h-6 side-svg"
              aria-hidden="true"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
